                    <p rend="center">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">4. japanese remaining to be repatriated</hi>
                    </p>
                    <p>Based on information available to Executive Headquarters, at the time the
                        residual repatriation mission was passed to the Army Advisory Group, the
                        following are the number of Japanese now remaining in China.</p>
                    <table cols="2" rows="8">
